-- Legg Mason CFO says will report lease write-offs
-- 
-- Fri Feb 1, 2013 8:52am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2013/02/01/us-leggmason-results-lease-idUSBRE9100Q620130201

 

 (Reuters) - Legg Mason Inc ( LM.N ) Chief Financial Officer Peter Nachtwey said the company will report lease write-off charges in the current quarter of $45 million to $55 million. Nachtwey spoke on a conference call with investors on Friday. 
 (Reporting By  Ross Kerber ; Editing by Gerald E. McCormick)